<para style="q1">

<verse number="15" style="v" />The eyes of Yahweh are on the righteous</para>

<para style="q1">and his ears are directed toward their cry.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />The face of Yahweh is against those who do evil,</para>

<para style="q1">to cut off the memory of them from the earth.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />The righteous cry out and Yahweh hears</para>

<para style="q1">and he rescues them from all their troubles.</para>
